Manga University 101 Privacy Policy
Manga University 101 Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Overview
This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is handled in the Manga University 101 mobile application for iOS.
We Collect No Personal Information Using Manga University 101
We do not collect, use, save, or have access to any of your personal data recorded in Manga University 101.
Individual settings relating to Manga University 101 are not personal and are stored only on your device.
Manga University 101 might ask you to provide access to your photo library, but this is only so you can save the drawings you create in Manga University 101 to your photo library. We don’t process that information and have no access to it.
Manga University 101 allows you to visit our website and our pages on social media sites, and our product pages in the Apple Books store and Amazon. Manga University 101 does not track or record any of those visits.
Manga University 101 complies with the U.S. Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act
Manga University 101 doesn’t collect personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:
privacy@mangauniversity.com
